==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: maldanian
<hw>mal*da"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of marine annelids of the genus <gen>Maldane</gen>, or
family <fam>Maldanidae</fam>. They have a slender, round body, and make
tubes in the sand or mud.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mal de mer</ent>⟦br⟧
